<section class="features-strip" id="features">
  <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon-wrap"><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt-lightning"></i></div><h3>自动部署，打开即用</h3><p>支持 Mac & Windows，内置国产优质大模型，支持切换自定义模型</p><span class="feature-tag">开箱即用</span></div>
  <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon-wrap"><i class="fa-brands fa-weixin" style="color:#07C160;"></i></div><h3>微信直接对话，远程操控</h3><p>直接关联微信，零配置，随时随地远程让 AI 干活</p><span class="feature-tag">微信直联</span></div>
  <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon-wrap"><i class="fa-solid fa-puzzle-piece"></i></div><h3>丰富 Skills 生态</h3><p>支持Skills市场，如ClawHub、GitHub 等丰富生态，Skills 随取随用</p><span class="feature-tag">丰富生态</span></div>
  <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon-wrap"><span style="font-size:22px;">🦞</span></div><h3>持续记忆，你的专属龙虾</h3><p>记住偏好和上下文，持续成长，越来越懂你的 AI</p><span class="feature-tag">懂你所想</span></div>
  <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon-wrap"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved" style="color:#07C160;"></i></div><h3>本地部署，办公更高效</h3><p>直接操控文件、浏览器、邮件，不是只会聊天</p><span class="feature-tag">高效操控</span></div>
</section>

<section class="how-section" id="how">
  <div class="section-header reveal"><div class="section-label"><span class="line"></span>HOW IT WORKS<span class="line"></span></div><h2>三步上手</h2><p>从下载到开始干活，几分钟即可上手</p></div>
  <div class="steps-row reveal">
