    <div class="step-item"><div class="step-icon-wrap"><div class="step-num">3</div>🚀</div><h3>微信或电脑发指令，开干</h3><p>通过微信或电脑发消息<br>QClaw 立刻帮你执行任务</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="demos" id="demos">
  <div class="section-header reveal"><div class="section-label"><span class="line"></span>USE CASES<span class="line"></span></div><h2>真实场景，即刻体验</h2><p>从日常提醒到自动化开发，QClaw 帮你解锁无限可能</p></div>
  <div class="demos-grid">
    <div class="demo-card reveal"><div class="demo-card-image"><div class="demo-visual scene-remote"><div class="hex-pattern"></div><i class="demo-scene-icon fa-solid fa-desktop"></i><div class="demo-mockup"><div class="chat-bubble user"><div class="wechat-tag"><i class="fa-brands fa-weixin"></i> 微信</div>帮我打开桌面的"Q3报告.xlsx"，把第3列数据求和</div><div class="chat-bubble bot">📂 已打开文件<br>✅ Q3总销售额为 ¥2,847,600，已保存！<span class="typing-cursor"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="demo-card-content"><span class="demo-tag">💻 远程操控</span><h3>远程操作电脑文件/网页</h3><p>不带电脑也能随时改文档、查数据、处理工作</p></div></div>
    <div class="demo-card reveal"><div class="demo-card-image"><div class="demo-visual scene-social"><div class="hex-pattern"></div><i class="demo-scene-icon fa-solid fa-folder-open"></i><div class="demo-mockup"><div class="chat-bubble user"><div class="wechat-tag"><i class="fa-brands fa-weixin"></i> 微信</div>帮我整理桌面上所有文档，按项目分类，每个项目提炼一页摘要</div><div class="chat-bubble bot">📂 已扫描桌面 86 个文件<br>🗂 已按 5 个项目自动归类<br>📝 每个项目摘要已生成 → summary.pdf<span class="typing-cursor"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="demo-card-content"><span class="demo-tag">📁 资料整理</span><h3>整理电脑资料并提炼</h3><p>自动归类文件、提炼关键信息，告别杂乱桌面</p></div></div>
    <div class="demo-card reveal"><div class="demo-card-image"><div class="demo-visual scene-weather"><div class="hex-pattern"></div><i class="demo-scene-icon fa-solid fa-cloud-sun-rain"></i><div class="demo-mockup"><div class="chat-bubble user"><div class="wechat-tag"><i class="fa-brands fa-weixin"></i> 微信</div>帮我设置每天早上 8 点推送天气</div><div class="chat-bubble bot">✅ 已设置！明早 8 点准时播报<br>🌤 明天晴，23°C，建议穿薄外套~<br>🌧 后天有雨，记得带伞哦</div></div></div></div><div class="demo-card-content"><span class="demo-tag">☀️ 智能提醒</span><h3>每日天气定时提醒</h3><p>自动推送天气状况，给出穿衣 & 出行建议</p></div></div>
    <div class="demo-card reveal"><div class="demo-card-image"><div class="demo-visual" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e0a0a,#2e1a0a);"><div class="hex-pattern"></div><i class="demo-scene-icon fa-solid fa-shrimp"></i><div class="demo-mockup"><div class="chat-bubble user"><div class="wechat-tag"><i class="fa-brands fa-weixin"></i> 微信</div>以后帮我写的邮件都用正式语气，结尾加"此致敬礼"</div><div class="chat-bubble bot">🦞 收到，已更新你的邮件风格偏好<br>✍️ 以后写邮件自动按这个风格来<br>📈 你的龙虾已学会 12 个偏好，持续进化中</div></div></div></div><div class="demo-card-content"><span class="demo-tag">🦞 养虾</span><h3>你的龙虾，越养越聪明</h3><p>持续学习你的风格和偏好，从通用助手进化为你的专属搭档</p></div></div>
    <div class="demo-card reveal"><div class="demo-card-image"><div class="demo-visual scene-github"><div class="hex-pattern"></div><i class="demo-scene-icon fa-brands fa-github"></i><div class="demo-mockup"><div class="chat-bubble user"><div class="wechat-tag"><i class="fa-brands fa-weixin"></i> 微信</div>帮我创建一个 Chrome 插件项目，自动提交到 GitHub</div><div class="chat-bubble bot">🛠 项目已创建：qclaw-chrome-ext<br>📦 已 push 到 GitHub，自动生成 README<br>⭐ 已自动生成 README 和文档</div></div></div></div><div class="demo-card-content"><span class="demo-tag">🚀 自动开发</span><h3>GitHub 项目自动开发</h3><p>你出创意，我来实现，自动建库写代码</p></div></div>
    <div class="demo-card reveal"><div class="demo-card-image"><div class="demo-visual scene-paper"><div class="hex-pattern"></div><i class="demo-scene-icon fa-solid fa-graduation-cap"></i><div class="demo-mockup"><div class="chat-bubble user"><div class="wechat-tag"><i class="fa-brands fa-weixin"></i> 微信</div>搜近3年 LLM Agent 综述论文，整理成文献综述</div><div class="chat-bubble bot">🔍 已检索到相关论文<br>📋 已按引用量筛选核心文献<br>📝 综述草稿已完成，引用格式：APA<br>✅ 已导出 PDF & LaTeX<span class="typing-cursor"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="demo-card-content"><span class="demo-tag">📚 学术研究</span><h3>学术论文自动整理</h3><p>自动找文献、整理引用、写综述、提升发文效率</p></div></div>
  </div>
</section>


